  "title": "feat(menu): Searchable menu widget",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nAdds searchable props to the `menu` widget similar to `refinement-list`. This change adds additional properties to `connectMenu` and `menu`, as well as adding the relevant search templates. This will be used by the new merchandising console with the upgrade to `react-instantsearch-hooks`. They currently use the searchable `menu` component in `react-instantsearch-dom`. \r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\nStories:\r\n/story/refinements-menu--with-search\r\n/story/refinements-menu--with-search-and-show-more\r\n\r\nScreenshot: \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69921547/194095030-5e8c6a65-b492-4d32-9a75-8e8b2acd2526.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nfixes #2893",
